Interface ToStringFunction.StackPrinter

Enclosing interface:
ToStringFunction<T>
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public static interface ToStringFunction.StackPrinter
A StackTraceElement array formatter for display as String Uses ToStringFunction.Arrays.toString(String, Object[], String, String, int, int) and references the next variables:
  • ToStringFunction.StackPrinter.Params.prefix
  • ToStringFunction.StackPrinter.Params.join
  • ToStringFunction.StackPrinter.Params.suffix
These variables can be changed at any given time.
